</b></p>
<p><b>Criminal Court and to fully align its legislation with all the obligations under 
</b></p>
<p><b>the Rome Statute including incorporating the Rome Statute definition of crimes 
</b></p>
<p><b>and general principles, as well as adopting provisions enabling cooperation 
</b></p>
<p><b>with the Court (Latvia); 
