procedure (Slovakia)/Consider ratifying other international human rights 
</b></p>
<p><b>instruments to which it is not a party yet (Nicaragua)/ Study the possibility of 
</b></p>
<p><b>ratifying the International Convention for the Protection of All Persons from 
</b></p>
<p><b>Enforced Disappearance (Argentina)/ Reconsider ratifying the International 
</b></p>
<p><b>Convention for the Protection of All Persons from Enforced Disappearance 
</b></p>
